1
00:00:23,763 --> 00:00:25,682
[NARRATOR]
Threatened by a ruthless demon,

2
00:00:25,765 --> 00:00:28,560
humanity was on the
brink of destruction.

3
00:00:32,105 --> 00:00:34,441
[NARRATOR] All seemed lost
until a lone mage

4
00:00:34,524 --> 00:00:36,985
stepped forward and
took up the fight.

5
00:00:43,533 --> 00:00:45,535
[NARRATOR]
After his triumph, he was hailed

6
00:00:45,618 --> 00:00:49,664
as the Wizard King,
and his story became legend.

7
00:00:51,291 --> 00:00:53,752
[NARRATOR] Driven by rage,
the elves who'd been reborn

8
00:00:53,835 --> 00:00:56,838
as Magic Knights continued
their vicious attack.

9
00:00:56,921 --> 00:00:59,758
As the Black Bulls hurried
to defend the royal capital,

10
00:00:59,841 --> 00:01:03,053
they crossed paths with
Sally, Rades, and Valtos,

11
00:01:03,136 --> 00:01:05,138
who had narrowly escaped
death when Licht

12
00:01:05,221 --> 00:01:07,265
unexpectedly used
them as a sacrifice

13
00:01:07,349 --> 00:01:09,351
to resurrect his elven brethren.

14
00:01:09,434 --> 00:01:11,478
[RADES]
You get on my nerves, too.

15
00:01:11,561 --> 00:01:15,106
But my first priority is
killing off that bastard, Licht.

16
00:01:15,190 --> 00:01:17,192
[NARRATOR] After some
convincing, the trio found

17
00:01:17,275 --> 00:01:18,777
common ground with
the Black Bulls

18
00:01:18,860 --> 00:01:20,445
and joined their cause.

19
00:01:20,528 --> 00:01:22,072
Meanwhile, at the castle,

20
00:01:22,155 --> 00:01:24,240
Noelle's determination
to save her siblings

21
00:01:24,324 --> 00:01:26,618
and protect the capital
motivated her to learn

22
00:01:26,701 --> 00:01:28,912
an awe-inspiring new technique.

23
00:01:28,995 --> 00:01:30,872
[NOELLE]
It's over!

24
00:01:32,082 --> 00:01:34,334
Langris, no!

25
00:01:34,417 --> 00:01:36,503
[NARRATOR]
As for Finral...

26
00:01:40,423 --> 00:01:42,842
Your brother! Wake up!

27
00:01:44,511 --> 00:01:46,221
Fallen Angel's Wingbeat!

28
00:01:47,806 --> 00:01:50,892
[FINRAL]
This is my last chance!

29
00:01:50,975 --> 00:01:52,268
Your big brother really shines

30
00:01:52,352 --> 00:01:55,105
when it comes to
speed and accuracy.

31
00:01:55,188 --> 00:01:58,566
So I'll stop you,
whatever it takes!

32
00:01:58,650 --> 00:02:02,320
I hope you're ready. Wake up!

33
00:02:02,404 --> 00:02:04,114
[NARRATOR]
He finally found a way to quell

34
00:02:04,197 --> 00:02:08,702
the destructive rampage of
his possessed brother, Langris.

35
00:02:08,785 --> 00:02:12,038
But, once Patry returned
to the hideout,

36
00:02:12,122 --> 00:02:14,958
he began to put a
terrifying plan into motion.

37
00:02:15,041 --> 00:02:17,794
[PATRY] Now all that's left
is to fit the final magic stone

38
00:02:17,877 --> 00:02:20,046
into the pedestal
within the castle,

39
00:02:20,130 --> 00:02:23,675
and initiate the spell that
will destroy the Clover Kingdom.

40
00:02:23,758 --> 00:02:27,137
After humanity is snuffed
out, we will reclaim

41
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:31,474
this world, making it a peaceful
place for elves alone.

42
00:02:31,558 --> 00:02:33,143
Roger that.

43
00:02:33,226 --> 00:02:37,731
As soon as these two wake up,
all the actors'll be on stage.

44
00:04:22,544 --> 00:04:23,670
Hey there.

45
00:04:23,753 --> 00:04:26,423
How do you feel after
that nice long nap?

46
00:04:26,506 --> 00:04:30,260
So, do you two remember?
What your old names were?

47
00:04:30,343 --> 00:04:31,594
Who you worked for?

48
00:04:31,678 --> 00:04:35,098
Yeah. We made up the
Third Eye, as I recall.

49
00:04:35,181 --> 00:04:38,184
Fana the Hateful,
and Vetto the Despair,

50
00:04:38,268 --> 00:04:41,479
and you were called Rhya the
Disloyal, isn't that right?

51
00:04:41,563 --> 00:04:43,523
How funny.

52
00:04:43,606 --> 00:04:45,316
[NARRATOR]
As the Eye of the Midnight Sun's

53
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:48,111
most formidable warriors,
the Third Eye had fought

54
00:04:48,194 --> 00:04:51,656
multiple battles against Asta
and his friends in the past.

55
00:04:51,740 --> 00:04:53,992
Vetto was killed,
and Fana's soul

56
00:04:54,075 --> 00:04:56,953
became separated from the
body it had been inhabiting,

57
00:04:57,037 --> 00:05:00,832
which, in turn, allowed that
body to begin a new life.

58
00:05:00,915 --> 00:05:03,168
Rhya preserved the
general characteristics

59
00:05:03,251 --> 00:05:06,171
of the human bodies the
other two had been using,

60
00:05:06,254 --> 00:05:09,799
and prepared two new vessels
for their souls to possess.

61
00:05:09,883 --> 00:05:11,634
[RHYA]
Welcome back, guys.

62
00:05:11,718 --> 00:05:13,887
I could only incubate
you for so long,

63
00:05:13,970 --> 00:05:16,389
so your bodies are
about 15 years old.

64
00:05:16,473 --> 00:05:19,476
Which means you're smaller
than me for a change, Vetto.

65
00:05:19,559 --> 00:05:21,853
Well, seeing as how
I've already died twice,

66
00:05:21,936 --> 00:05:22,979
this'll do fine.

67
00:05:23,063 --> 00:05:24,022
Agreed.

68
00:05:24,105 --> 00:05:25,899
Creating near-identical bodies

69
00:05:25,982 --> 00:05:28,526
with the same mana
as the originals.

70
00:05:28,610 --> 00:05:30,111
I gotta say,

71
00:05:30,195 --> 00:05:33,698
Sally's really outdone herself
with her research on this one.

72
00:05:33,782 --> 00:05:35,408
I'd compliment her,
but she's probably

73
00:05:35,492 --> 00:05:37,077
been dead for a while now.

74
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:40,955
[FANA] My mind is a lot
clearer this time around, too.

75
00:05:41,039 --> 00:05:42,749
Oh, I can explain that.

76
00:05:42,832 --> 00:05:46,336
See, last round, we used the
evil eye to bring you back,

77
00:05:46,419 --> 00:05:49,673
so I'm sure your malice
was a lot stronger before.

78
00:05:49,756 --> 00:05:52,676
Evil eye? That's right.

79
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:55,387
I did feel
half-asleep back then.

80
00:05:55,470 --> 00:05:59,849
It was almost like I was having
some terrible nightmare.

81
00:05:59,933 --> 00:06:02,435
Salamander!

82
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:04,020
There's no response.

83
00:06:04,104 --> 00:06:06,773
I guess I must not
have it anymore.

84
00:06:06,856 --> 00:06:08,483
[RHYA] That means
it found somebody else

85
00:06:08,566 --> 00:06:10,318
who was qualified
while Fana was gone

86
00:06:10,402 --> 00:06:13,196
and partnered up
with them instead.

87
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:15,990
[RHYA] Eh, it's fine.
Even without Salamander,

88
00:06:16,074 --> 00:06:17,826
you're strong enough
as you are now.

89
00:06:17,909 --> 00:06:19,202
Yeah, that's true.

90
00:06:19,285 --> 00:06:21,871
There's no way I'd let
those humans beat me!

91
00:06:21,955 --> 00:06:22,872
[VETTO gasps]

92
00:06:22,956 --> 00:06:24,457
'Kay, the next step
is to take you

93
00:06:24,541 --> 00:06:25,792
over to the Grimoire Tower.

94
00:06:25,875 --> 00:06:27,961
The sooner you let one
pick you out, the better.

95
00:06:28,044 --> 00:06:31,631
Before that,
we need some clothes.

96
00:06:31,715 --> 00:06:34,968
Especially for her. And quick.

97
00:06:35,051 --> 00:06:36,845
He's right. Now that
I take a good look,

98
00:06:36,928 --> 00:06:39,014
I think you're more
developed than last time.

99
00:06:39,097 --> 00:06:40,306
Good for y--

100
00:06:50,692 --> 00:06:53,611
Before too long,
this false royal capital

101
00:06:53,695 --> 00:06:56,823
constructed by the humans
will be no more.

102
00:06:56,906 --> 00:07:00,076
[FRAGIL] They've finally
gathered up above.

103
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,911
[KLAUS] Then they must've
received the revelation

104
00:07:01,995 --> 00:07:04,247
in preparation for this moment.

105
00:07:06,166 --> 00:07:08,126
[ELVES]
Those who guide the elves.

106
00:07:08,209 --> 00:07:10,378
The Apostles of Sephira!

107
00:07:19,346 --> 00:07:20,847
Licht, it's you!

108
00:07:24,559 --> 00:07:27,520
He's not saying much,
but I can guarantee

109
00:07:27,604 --> 00:07:29,773
you he's in there
somewhere, deep down.

110
00:07:29,856 --> 00:07:31,983
Trust me, Patry, as soon
as the reincarnation

111
00:07:32,067 --> 00:07:35,070
is complete, you'll see
the old Licht again.

112
00:07:35,153 --> 00:07:39,532
I understand. Wait,
what about that boy?

113
00:07:39,616 --> 00:07:42,118
[RHYA]
Oh, yeah, that was weird.

114
00:07:42,202 --> 00:07:44,245
He was reincarnated
like us, but somehow,

115
00:07:44,329 --> 00:07:46,873
he still kept the
human's personality.

116
00:07:46,956 --> 00:07:48,291
Are you serious?

117
00:07:48,375 --> 00:07:49,668
[RHYA]
Don't sweat it.

118
00:07:49,751 --> 00:07:52,295
He'll come around, too,
when everything's finished.

119
00:07:52,379 --> 00:07:54,589
Let's go and wait over there.

120
00:07:54,673 --> 00:07:55,799
[PATRY]
Okay.

121
00:07:59,386 --> 00:08:02,055
[RHYA]
Man, get a load of this view!

122
00:08:02,138 --> 00:08:04,974
The party's in full swing.

123
00:08:05,058 --> 00:08:07,435
Now then, let's get started.

124
00:08:12,899 --> 00:08:15,485
[RHYA] By infusing
Gravito Stones with magic,

125
00:08:15,568 --> 00:08:17,779
we'll open the door
below Clover Castle,

126
00:08:17,862 --> 00:08:20,448
and release the seal
on the underworld!

127
00:08:20,532 --> 00:08:21,991
[gasps]

128
00:08:22,075 --> 00:08:24,119
What the hell is that?

129
00:08:29,332 --> 00:08:31,334
This doesn't look good.

130
00:08:31,418 --> 00:08:34,546
[NOELLE] Nozel, what's
happening to the castle?

131
00:08:34,629 --> 00:08:37,674
[MIMOSA]
I don't understand this at all!

132
00:08:37,757 --> 00:08:40,218
[BAVAL] This is a magic space
that serves as a border

133
00:08:40,301 --> 00:08:42,303
between this world and
the next, which the elves

134
00:08:42,387 --> 00:08:45,056
entrusted to the humans
through an ancient pact.

135
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:47,308
It's called the Shadow Palace.

136
00:08:47,392 --> 00:08:50,437
It can only be opened by
the Apostles of Sephira.

137
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:55,358
Ten elves who can receive
divine messages. See?

138
00:08:55,442 --> 00:08:57,318
When we place the
final magic stone

139
00:08:57,402 --> 00:08:59,654
into its pedestal
inside the palace,

140
00:08:59,738 --> 00:09:02,782
the elves' great reincarnation
will be complete!

141
00:09:02,866 --> 00:09:06,036
Of course, a price must be paid
for our use of these bodies.

142
00:09:06,119 --> 00:09:11,207
Sadly, their human souls will
be sent to the underworld!

143
00:09:11,291 --> 00:09:12,584
Think again!

144
00:09:12,667 --> 00:09:16,379
As an envoy of beauty,
I won't allow such ugliness!

145
00:09:22,093 --> 00:09:23,470
[MIMOSA]
David's Dice Magic gives him

146
00:09:23,553 --> 00:09:25,805
various advantages,
with higher rolls

147
00:09:25,889 --> 00:09:27,849
being the most devastating!

148
00:09:27,932 --> 00:09:30,685
But, getting this
much power from a two?

149
00:09:30,769 --> 00:09:32,937
It doesn't make sense!

150
00:09:33,021 --> 00:09:35,440
It won't do you any
good to attack me,

151
00:09:35,523 --> 00:09:38,234
but you might as well
give it a shot.

152
00:09:38,318 --> 00:09:41,863
[MIMOSA gasps]
How are we going to fix this?

153
00:09:44,074 --> 00:09:45,575
[YAMI]
'Kay, so there's a magical

154
00:09:45,658 --> 00:09:47,452
space growin' over there.

155
00:09:47,535 --> 00:09:52,123
I don't really get the details,
but it's definitely bad news.

156
00:09:52,207 --> 00:09:55,126
[cackles] Sounds like our
cue to head that way.

157
00:09:55,210 --> 00:09:56,586
Huh?

158
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:03,468
[KLAUS] You won't stop
the Apostles of Sephira!

159
00:10:03,551 --> 00:10:04,969
I get the feelin'
they're not plannin'

160
00:10:05,053 --> 00:10:06,221
to cooperate with us.

161
