but it's fine, I promise!

195
00:11:43,109 --> 00:11:44,527
Hey, look.

196
00:11:44,611 --> 00:11:48,782
What's with... that black...
castle... back there?

197
00:11:48,865 --> 00:11:51,701
Looks like Gauche is chillin'
on top of the enemy base!

198
