203
00:12:06,466 --> 00:12:08,134
[YAMI]
There's our Henry.

204
00:12:08,218 --> 00:12:11,596
[laughs] Ya buncha dumbasses!

205
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:13,431
Better work on that entrance!

206
00:12:13,515 --> 00:12:16,559
Captain! Sorry to make you wait!

207
00:12:16,643 --> 00:12:19,312
Whoa, Finral's behind him,
totally passed out!

208
00:12:19,396 --> 00:12:21,815
Oh, no! I didn't even know
you woke up the first time--

209
00:12:21,898 --> 00:12:24,693
you can't turn around and go
back to sleep already, Finral!

210
00:12:24,776 --> 00:12:26,194
You'd better not
make us check you

211
00:12:26,277 --> 00:12:28,988
into the infirmary again
after you just got out!

212
00:12:29,072 --> 00:12:30,365
My cooking'll get everybody

213
