our slack!" you lazy idiots!

218
00:12:41,751 --> 00:12:44,504
[NOELLE]
Ugh, it was terrifying!

219
00:12:44,587 --> 00:12:47,007
[ASTA] Whoa, what's with
the new outfit, Noelle?

220
00:12:47,090 --> 00:12:48,550
You look extra cool now!

221
00:12:48,633 --> 00:12:50,010
[MAGNA]
Hey, you're the ones who almost

222
00:12:50,093 --> 00:12:51,344
got your butts kicked!

223
00:12:51,428 --> 00:12:53,346
You should be
thankin' us, princess!

224
00:12:53,430 --> 00:12:55,265
You care to explain
the walking house

225
00:12:55,348 --> 00:12:56,725
full of loud people?

226
00:12:56,808 --> 00:12:59,269
I wish I could, but this
is new for me, too.

227
00:12:59,352 --> 00:13:01,813
It seems like our squad
gets weirder every day.

228
00:13:01,896 --> 00:13:04,065
But everything's
gonna be okay now,

229
00:13:04,149 --> 00:13:06,693
because all of the
Black Bulls are here!

230
00:13:06,776 --> 00:13:08,611
[KLAUS]
Curse you, humans!

231
00:13:08,695 --> 00:13:10,697
Bring in whatever
reinforcements you like,

232
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:13,116
you're still no match
for the elves!

233
00:13:14,576 --> 00:13:15,744
Ready?

234
00:13:22,125 --> 00:13:24,586
[LUCK] This spell gauges
the strength of their attack,

235
00:13:24,669 --> 00:13:26,713
and then together...

236
00:13:26,796 --> 00:13:29,090
[LUCK, MAGNA, GORDON, SALLY]
...we intercept it!

237
00:13:32,010 --> 00:13:33,970
[KLAUS groans]

238
00:13:34,054 --> 00:13:35,638
So cool!

239
00:13:35,722 --> 00:13:37,599
[RADES]
Now where's your leader?

240
00:13:37,682 --> 00:13:39,934
That's enough! Take this!

241
00:13:40,018 --> 00:13:40,769
C'mon, Rouge!

242
00:13:40,852 --> 00:13:42,312
[meows]

243
00:13:47,275 --> 00:13:51,613
[KLAUS gasps] What happened?
Our attacks aren't landing!

244
00:13:51,696 --> 00:13:54,574
Here... goes!

245
