[BOTH yelling]

246
00:13:57,869 --> 00:13:59,454
Good, now hurry and chow down

247
00:13:59,537 --> 00:14:03,500
so you can replenish all
the mana you just used!

248
00:14:03,583 --> 00:14:05,960
[ASTA] I can't use magic,
but I'm gonna eat anyway!

249
00:14:06,044 --> 00:14:07,837
[RADES]
I don't see Licht anywhere!

250
00:14:07,921 --> 00:14:09,339
Ha! Look at 'em,
havin' a snack

251
00:14:09,422 --> 00:14:10,757
in the middle of a fight!

252
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,133
So what do you think of my team?

253
00:14:12,217 --> 00:14:13,968
Pretty tough, aren't they?

254
00:14:14,052 --> 00:14:15,679
I wanna cut them.

255
00:14:15,762 --> 00:14:18,056
[YAMI]
Whoa. Well, don't!

256
00:14:19,599 --> 00:14:22,143
Really? The Black Bulls?

257
00:14:22,227 --> 00:14:25,063
Even here, they stand in my way.

258
00:14:25,146 --> 00:14:29,067
That one's magic interferes
with the very laws of nature.

259
00:14:29,150 --> 00:14:30,944
So she's a witch!

260
00:14:31,027 --> 00:14:34,656
It would appear their defense
largely depends on her.

261
00:14:34,739 --> 00:14:37,492
[DOROTHY]
I'm going now. Goodbye.

262
00:14:37,575 --> 00:14:38,535
Oh, Reve!

263
00:14:38,618 --> 00:14:41,579
Ah. I see, so you're
finally awake.

264
00:14:41,663 --> 00:14:45,166
I can't believe it--you sleep
even more than Rhya does.

265
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:46,376
You gonna be okay?

266
00:14:46,459 --> 00:14:48,336
This'll be your first
spell in centuries,

267
00:14:48,420 --> 00:14:50,672
your past life included.

268
00:14:50,755 --> 00:14:54,050
Who, me? Yes. I'm fine.

269
00:14:54,134 --> 00:14:56,761
[MIMOSA]
Black Bulls, can you hear me?

270
00:14:56,845 --> 00:14:58,138
[ASTA]
Mimosa's here, with her brother

271
00:14:58,221 --> 00:14:59,681
and that mushroom guy.

272
00:14:59,764 --> 00:15:00,932
If we don't do something,

273
00:15:01,016 --> 00:15:02,559
all of the Magic Knights
who've been possessed

274
00:15:02,642 --> 00:15:04,894
are going to lose
their souls forever!

275
00:15:04,978 --> 00:15:07,188
We're running out of time, Asta!

276
00:15:07,272 --> 00:15:08,773
Seriously?

277
00:15:10,066 --> 00:15:13,194
[BLACK BULLS gasp]

278
00:15:13,278 --> 00:15:16,072
My! Such magnificent magic!

279
00:15:16,156 --> 00:15:18,575
Don't tell me this ki
is what I think it is.

280
00:15:18,658 --> 00:15:21,661
[ASTA gasps]
I know her!

281
00:15:23,413 --> 00:15:25,874
That's the captain
of the Coral Peacocks!

282
00:15:25,957 --> 00:15:28,668
Did she get possessed, too?

283
00:15:28,752 --> 00:15:32,130
[DOROTHY]
Dream Magic: Glamour World.

284
00:15:35,508 --> 00:15:39,095
No way! What did she do?

285
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:43,683
[HENRY] I can sense the magic
of the pieces that vanished,

286
00:15:43,767 --> 00:15:46,186
but they don't exist anywhere.

287
00:15:46,269 --> 00:15:48,271
[ASTA]
Hey, we're missing some people!

288
00:15:48,355 --> 00:15:51,191
Vanessa, Magna,
Luck, Charmy, Sally!

289
00:15:51,274 --> 00:15:52,567
What did she do with everyone?

290
00:15:52,650 --> 00:15:53,860
It's gorgeous!

291
00:15:53,943 --> 00:15:55,320
But the moment she activates it,

292
00:15:55,403 --> 00:15:57,697
her targets will cease
to exist in this world!

293
00:15:57,781 --> 00:16:00,200
They've been whisked away
to the World of Dreams.

294
00:16:00,283 --> 00:16:01,576
And once you're in,
there's nothing

295
00:16:01,659 --> 00:16:03,119
you can do to get out!

296
00:16:03,203 --> 00:16:06,373
There is. There must be!

297
00:16:06,456 --> 00:16:09,000
Well, I suppose that takes
care of their defense.

298
00:16:09,084 --> 00:16:11,628
All right, let's wrap
things up then.

299
00:16:11,711 --> 00:16:13,088
[BLACK BULLS gasp]

300
00:16:16,633 --> 00:16:17,759
[PATRY, GAUCHE]
Combo Spell:

301
00:16:17,842 --> 00:16:20,220
Light Sword Storm of
Imperial Conviction.

302
00:16:20,303 --> 00:16:24,099
[BLACK BULLS yelling]

303
00:16:24,182 --> 00:16:27,727
Ha! There you are,
Licht! Fight me!

304
00:16:27,811 --> 00:16:29,813
And there's Gauche, too!

305
00:16:29,896 --> 00:16:32,565
Hey, Gordon, could you please
do that one thing now?

306
00:16:32,649 --> 00:16:34,192
Okay!

307
00:16:34,275 --> 00:16:38,071
Poison Curse Magic:
Dwelling of the Poison Cloud!

308
00:16:38,154 --> 00:16:42,075
[ASTA] Whoa, wait! I don't see
how this is gonna help!

309
00:16:42,158 --> 00:16:44,035
[GREY]
Don't worry, I can fix it!

310
00:16:44,119 --> 00:16:46,871
Conversion Magic:
Poison to Cotton!

311
00:16:46,955 --> 00:16:49,124
[ASTA yelps]

312
00:16:49,207 --> 00:16:50,625
[ASTA]
Whew, that was close!

313
00:16:50,709 --> 00:16:52,335
Thanks for savin'
everyone, Grey!

314
00:16:52,419 --> 00:16:53,712
[GREY whimpering]

315
00:16:53,795 --> 00:16:56,131
What, were you tryin' to do,
poison the whole squad?

316
00:16:56,214 --> 00:16:58,174
[mumbling] I was using
teamwork to help my friends

317
00:16:58,258 --> 00:17:00,010
in their time of need.

318
00:17:00,093 --> 00:17:01,845
[GAUCHE]
We can handle things here.

319
00:17:01,928 --> 00:17:04,723
Why don't you go ahead and meet
up with your precious Licht?

320
00:17:04,806 --> 00:17:07,017
I wish you wouldn't
say it like that.

321
00:17:07,100 --> 00:17:09,602
But yes, I'm counting
on you, Droit.

322
00:17:09,686 --> 00:17:12,230
Sure. I'll catch ya later.

323
00:17:15,150 --> 00:17:18,570
Ugh! Hey, Valtos!
Make me a portal!

324
00:17:22,240 --> 00:17:24,284
Man, they're such jerks!

325
00:17:24,367 --> 00:17:33,209
[HENRY] Everyone...! You
should... get away... from me!

326
00:17:33,293 --> 00:17:36,004
[ASTA]
Henry! He got too far away

327
00:17:36,087 --> 00:17:37,630
from the Raging Black Bull!

328
00:17:37,714 --> 00:17:39,466
And without Charmy,
nobody can recharge

329
00:17:39,549 --> 00:17:42,093
their mana if it runs out!

330
00:17:42,177 --> 00:17:43,887
[NOELLE]
You guys!

331
00:17:47,307 --> 00:17:49,726
My armor. It vanished!

332
00:17:49,809 --> 00:17:52,771
Well, that crazy spell of
yours was kind of a doozy.

333
00:17:52,854 --> 00:17:56,149
Your body probably can't
keep up with it just yet.

334
00:17:56,232 --> 00:17:57,400
[ZORA]
Now that I think of it,

335
00:17:57,484 --> 00:18:00,236
I'm runnin' pretty
low on juice myself.

336
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:01,488
Oh, Asta.

337
00:18:01,571 --> 00:18:04,115
Goodness, you look even
more feeble than usual!

338
00:18:04,199 --> 00:18:06,117
[YAMI] I know the Black
Bulls need my help,

339
00:18:06,201 --> 00:18:09,621
but I can't let the bossman
slip through my fingers.

340
00:18:09,704 --> 00:18:12,082
Don't screw this up,
you hear me?

341
00:18:12,165 --> 00:18:14,501
I want you to surpass
your damn limits!

342
00:18:14,584 --> 00:18:16,628
--[GREY] Uh, okay sir!
--[ASTA] Yeah!

343
00:18:16,711 --> 00:18:19,589
Sounds good! I'll see ya
in a little bit, then!

344
00:18:19,673 --> 00:18:21,800
Time to go, Jack!

345
00:18:21,883 --> 00:18:25,470
[JACK] Since when am I
taking orders from you?

346
00:18:25,553 --> 00:18:28,723
[MARIE] Look, Brother,
some of them are gone.

347
00:18:28,807 --> 00:18:30,517
[GAUCHE] Then we need to kill
the rest of them quickly

348
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:33,561
and hurry after
the ones who left.

349
00:18:33,645 --> 00:18:35,313
That's where you come in, Eclat.

350
00:18:35,397 --> 00:18:37,649
It's time for a fun
game of hide-and-seek.

351
00:18:37,732 --> 00:18:39,067
Right.

352
00:18:39,150 --> 00:18:42,153
[GAUCHE] Willpower won't be
enough to save them now.

353
00:18:50,495 --> 00:18:56,001
[MARIE] I found them.
Look at me, humans.

354
00:18:57,627 --> 00:18:58,837
[GAUCHE]
Mirror Magic...

355
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,338
[MARIE]
Eye Magic...

356
00:19:00,422 --> 00:19:03,591
[GAUCHE, MARIE]
Combo Spell: Reflect Iris.

357
00:19:03,675 --> 00:19:04,884
[gasps]

358
00:19:07,721 --> 00:19:09,472
[ASTA]
What's happening?

359
00:19:09,556 --> 00:19:11,266
[GREY]
Why can't I move?

360
00:19:11,349 --> 00:19:12,892
[GORDON]
We're stuck!

361
00:19:12,976 --> 00:19:15,603
[MIMOSA]
How is this possible?

362
00:19:15,687 --> 00:19:16,980
[NOELLE]
My magic...

363
00:19:17,063 --> 00:19:18,648
[ZORA grunts]

364
00:19:18,732 --> 00:19:20,942
Little Eclat has the
ability to immobilize

365
00:19:21,026 --> 00:19:23,028
anybody who looks into her eyes.

366
00:19:23,111 --> 00:19:26,322
It renders your magic
useless, as well.

367
00:19:26,406 --> 00:19:27,699
[ASTA]
What?

368
00:19:27,782 --> 00:19:30,744
But Marie doesn't even
have her grimoire yet!

369
00:19:30,827 --> 00:19:33,455
I guess the elves are
just that powerful!

370
00:19:33,538 --> 00:19:37,542
There's no hope for you.
Now die, helpless worms.

371
00:19:39,169 --> 00:19:42,589
[ASTA]
Not yet. I refuse to give up!

372
00:19:46,092 --> 00:19:48,803
[ASTA]
This is not the end!

373
00:19:48,887 --> 00:19:52,265
I still have to turn Gauche
and Marie back to normal,

374
00:19:52,349 --> 00:19:54,184
not to mention everyone else!

375
00:19:54,267 --> 00:19:58,688
I'll set things right.
No matter what it takes!

376
00:19:58,772 --> 00:20:04,652
[ASTA growls, yells]

377
00:20:04,736 --> 00:20:06,196
[gasps]

378
00:20:06,279 --> 00:20:09,824
Hey, look at that. I can move!

379
00:20:09,908 --> 00:20:12,577
He must've nullified the spell!

380
00:20:12,660 --> 00:20:16,373
Asta... you... did it!

381
00:20:16,456 --> 00:20:18,958
Okay, you guys! Everyone ready?

382
00:20:19,042 --> 00:20:20,627
--[GORDON] All set!
--[GREY] Yes!

383
00:20:20,710 --> 00:20:23,630
Hold on. That blade.

384
00:20:23,713 --> 00:20:26,549
Why does he have Licht's
Demon Destroyer Sword?

385
00:20:26,633 --> 00:20:28,802
You don't deserve that weapon!

386
00:20:28,885 --> 00:20:30,720
Give it back and die!

387
00:20:34,057 --> 00:20:36,101
[GREY]
I'll use Transformation Magic...

388
00:20:36,184 --> 00:20:38,144
Here!

389
00:20:38,228 --> 00:20:40,146
[GREY]
...to make more mirrors!

390
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:43,149
[GORDON]
Poison Magic: Forbidden Fruit!

391
00:20:47,028 --> 00:20:50,407
[ASTA growls, yells]

392
00:20:53,326 --> 00:20:55,328
[ASTA]
It may be stronger now,

393
00:20:55,412 --> 00:20:58,748
but I still understand
Gauche's magic really well!

394
00:20:58,832 --> 00:21:02,293
Actually, he kinda ticks me off!

395
00:21:02,377 --> 00:21:05,255
The way he used to shoot
those weird beams at me.

396
00:21:05,338 --> 00:21:06,798
You know, gettin'
possessed didn't change

397
00:21:06,881 --> 00:21:09,134
his personality much!

398
00:21:09,217 --> 00:21:11,469
Yes, I agree,
and after we save him,

399
00:21:11,553 --> 00:21:13,638
he'll go right back
to insulting us.

400
00:21:13,722 --> 00:21:15,098
That's exactly what'll happen,

401
00:21:15,181 --> 00:21:17,058
plus he'll keep showing us
pictures of his sister

402
00:21:17,142 --> 00:21:18,810
and making dolls of her
and getting nosebleeds

403
00:21:18,893 --> 00:21:20,020
when he thinks about her.

404
00:21:20,103 --> 00:21:21,980
He's really not a fun
person to be around!

405
00:21:22,063 --> 00:21:28,778
He's... always...
been... creepy!

406
00:21:28,862 --> 00:21:30,822
[ALL] That's why we need
to bring back the Gauche

407
00:21:30,905 --> 00:21:34,451
we all know, so we can
complain to his face!

408
00:23:11,047 --> 00:23:12,966
[FULL CAST]
Clover Clips!

409
00:23:15,218 --> 00:23:16,594
[RHYA]
"Revival."

410
00:23:18,388 --> 00:23:19,806
[RHYA]
Part 1.

411
00:23:24,185 --> 00:23:25,687
There's not much time.

412
00:23:25,770 --> 00:23:28,189
I was in a bit of a
rush to take you out,

413
00:23:28,273 --> 00:23:31,317
which means your bodies are
gonna be pretty puny now.

414
00:23:31,401 --> 00:23:33,653
[BOTH crying]

415
00:23:33,737 --> 00:23:37,657
[RHYA] Okay, I probably
shouldn't have jumped the gun.

416
00:23:37,741 --> 00:23:39,117
Part 2.

417
00:23:40,910 --> 00:23:44,497
[RHYA] I had plenty of time
to spare, so I let 'em steep.

418
00:23:44,581 --> 00:23:47,917
Vetto and Fana should be more
mature this time around.

419
00:23:49,711 --> 00:23:51,504
[VETTO] I don't know what
happened to me before...

420
00:23:51,588 --> 00:23:54,924
[RHYA] We gotta find some
kinda happy medium here!

421
00:23:56,843 --> 00:23:58,928
[GORDON]
My best friend, Gauche Adlai.

422
00:23:59,012 --> 00:24:01,598
Your little sister is
basically my little sister.

423
00:24:01,681 --> 00:24:04,601
That's right! Marie
is my actual sister!

424
00:24:04,684 --> 00:24:08,229
<i>Black Clover</i> , Page 111:
"The Eyes in the Mirror."

